description:
Strava makes fitness tracking social. We house your entire active journey in one spot – and you get to share it with friends. Here’s how:

• Record everything – runs, rides, hikes, yoga and over 30 other sport types. Think of Strava as the home of your movement.

• Discover anywhere – our Routes tool uses de-identified Strava data to intelligently recommend popular routes based on your preferences. You can also build your own.

• Build a support network – Strava’s about celebrating movement. Here you’ll find your community and cheer each other on.

• Train smarter – get data insights to understand your progress and see how you improve. Your Training Log is the record of all your workouts.

• Get more from your workout – Powered by AI, Athlete Intelligence turns workout data into into instant insights. Keeping you motivated and ready for the next workout – without the guesswork.

• Move safer – share your real-time location with loved ones while outdoors for an extra layer of safety.

• Sync your favourite apps and devices – Strava is compatible with thousands of them (Apple Watch, Fitbit, Garmin – you name it).

• Join and create challenges – join millions in monthly challenges to chase new goals, collect digital badges and stay accountable.

• Embrace the unfiltered – your feed on Strava is filled with real efforts from real people. That’s how we motivate each other.

• Whether you’re a world-class athlete or a total beginner, you belong here. Just record and go.

Strava includes both a free version and a subscription version with premium features.
Strava uses HealthKit to export your Strava activities into the Health app and to read heart rate and biometric data.

You can subscribe and pay on the App Store, using your Apple ID. Payment will be charged to your Apple ID at confirmation of purchase. Your subscription will automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renew may be turned off after purchase by going to the ‘Manage Subscription’ page in settings. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable. The subscription will renew at the same cost.

Terms of Service: https://www.strava.com/legal/terms
Privacy Policy: https://www.strava.com/legal/privacy

CO-FIT is a newly designed and developed app for our new smartwatch collection only.
main feature:
   Sync your steps, calories, mileage, heart rate, sleep and exercise records from your watch. The newly designed UI can display data more intuitively.
   After binding and authorization, we will push the phone's incoming calls and text messages to the watch to avoid losing information.
   You can use the app to configure the watch's sedentary alarms, alarms, schedules, backlighting, as well as sync weather and AGPS files (to help the watch locate) and other features for better use of the watch.
During use, if you have any questions, you can ask at any time, we will listen to your suggestions and make improvements.

Disclaimer:
1. The data displayed by the app is provided by the device, and the app only records and shares
2. All health data displayed in the app are not suitable for medical use, all health data are for reference only, these data should not be used as a substitute for the opinions of health care professionals
For accurate data, consult your doctor.

Authorization Instructions
1. We will access iPhone Health, sync device data to iPhone Health in real time
2. We will access the mobile phone location to obtain local weather information and synchronize it to the device display

Looking for a simple and reliable way to track your heart health and overall well-being? The PulseMate App helps you monitor your heart rate, track blood pressure trends, record blood sugar levels, log vital health data and get personalized healthy suggestions—all in one place, right from your iPhone.

Key features：
Heart rate measurement: Just place your finger lightly on the camera area of   your phone to measure your heart rate.

Blood sugar, blood pressure and temperature records: Conveniently record daily blood pressure, blood sugar and temperature data, PulseMate will generate detailed trend charts for you to help you track health changes.

AI Care: Talk to your dedicated AI health consultants anytime, anywhere. Personalized suggestions can help you make better daily health choices.

HRV analysis: Evaluate your overall health status by monitoring key indicators such as stress, energy and tension.

Drinking water record and reminder: Remind and record daily water intake to help you maintain adequate hydration.

Breathing exercise: Through scientific breathing exercises, it helps you relax, relieve stress and reduce anxiety.

Mental health test: Regularly evaluate mental health status to help you pay attention to your emotions and mental state in time.

Heart health risk test: Through a simple questionnaire, you can gain an in-depth understanding of your heart health status and provide personalized health suggestions.

Health data overview: Centrally view all daily health indicators, manage your health data in one stop, and easily grasp health trends.

How to measure heart rate：
Place your finger lightly on the iPhone's camera lens.
Maintain full coverage of the lens with your fingertip.
Hold steady throughout the duration of the measurement until completion.

Important reminder: 
This application is for personal monitoring and information reference only and is not a substitute for professional medical advice or treatment. If you feel any discomfort or other emergency, please seek medical assistance from a professional medical person immediately.

- Subscribe to get unlimited access to all premium features.
- Subscription length: weekly, yearly.
- The iTunes account will be charged after the trial period ends.
- You should be aware that the subscription will automatically renew unless you close the automatic renewal at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.
- After purchase, you can turn off automatic renewal at the account settings.

Combining Mi Fitness with smartwatch or smartband devices, users can track their health and fitness data. 

Mi Fitness supported：Xiaomi Watch Series, Redmi Watch Series, Xiaomi Smart Band Series, Redmi Smart Band Series.

Keep track of your workouts
Map your route, monitor your progress, and achieve your goals. Whether it's walking, running, or biking, you can easily track it right from your phone.
Monitor your health information*
Mi Fitness APP assists you in managing your personal health, helping you to always maintain your optimal state. By connecting Xiaomi or Redmi smartwatch/band devices, important health indicators such as heart rate, sleep, stress, and energy can be monitored and risk warnings generated throughout the day. Health data such as weight and women's health can also be manually recorded and managed.
Sleep better*
In conjunction with Xiaomi or Redmi smartwatch/band devices that has sleep monitoring functionality, you can record your sleep information every night. By conducting in-depth analysis of the different stages of sleep, including deep sleep, light sleep, and rapid eye movement, as well as monitoring your sleep heart rate, breathing quality, body movements, and other sleep-related data, the device generates a personalized sleep report. This report can help remind you to adjust your sleep habits in a timely manner.
Easy payments with wearable device
Link your Mastercard cards to Mi Fitness and enjoy the convenience of making payments on the go with your wearable device.
Ask Alexa for convenient access
With Alexa, you can easily access important features like checking the weather, playing music, and starting a workout. Just ask and you're good to go.
Stay informed with notifications
Receive notifications, messages, and emails directly on your wearable device, so you can stay informed without having to constantly check your phone.

*Disclaimer
Except for the manual health information recording service provided to users, all other health services within the application only synchronize and record the relevant information of the wristband or watch. All health-related data, results, suggestions, etc. are for reference only and are not intended for medical purposes, including self-diagnosis or consultation with a doctor, and are only used for general fitness and health purposes.
Please note that all smartwatches/fitness trackers currently integrated into the application are not medical devices and cannot provide any form of medical services. In case of any physical discomfort, please seek timely advice from medical institutions.

The BINFO Calorie Tracker is a versatile and user-friendly application designed to empower you in your journey toward better health and nutrition. With this app, you can:

1. Monitor Your Caloric Intake: Keep track of the calories you consume each day. Log your meals and snacks to gain insight into your dietary habits and make informed decisions about your calorie intake.

2. Plan Balanced Meals: Plan your meals in advance with the app's meal planning feature. Create daily or weekly meal plans and set calorie goals to help you achieve your dietary objectives.

3. Track Nutritional Information: Beyond just calories, the app provides detailed nutritional information for each food item you log. Explore macronutrients (carbohydrates, proteins, and fats), vitamins, minerals, and more to ensure a balanced diet.

4. Achieve Your Fitness Goals: Use the app to set and monitor your fitness goals, whether it's losing weight, gaining muscle, or maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Track your progress over time.

5. Stay Hydrated: Monitor your daily water intake to ensure you stay adequately hydrated. Proper hydration is essential for overall well-being.

6. Record Exercise Activities: Log your exercise routines and track the calories burned during workouts. The app can integrate with fitness devices and apps for more accurate data.

7. Customize Your Profile: Tailor the app to your unique needs and preferences by customizing your profile. Adjust your calorie targets based on your goals and dietary requirements.

8. Access an Extensive Food Database: The app includes an extensive database of foods and beverages, making it easy to find and log items, whether they're common groceries or specific restaurant dishes.

9. Visualize Your Progress: Use charts and graphs to visualize your progress over time. Track changes in your weight, calorie consumption, and nutritional intake to stay motivated and on course.

10. Connect with a Community: Depending on the version of the app, you might have access to a supportive community of like-minded individuals. Share your progress, seek advice, and offer support to others on their health and fitness journeys.

11. Ensure Data Security: Rest easy knowing that your sensitive health information is secure. The app typically employs robust security measures and complies with privacy regulations to protect your data.
In summary, the BINFO Calorie Tracker is a comprehensive tool to help you take control of your diet, improve your nutrition, and work toward your fitness and weight management goals. Whether you want to shed a few pounds, maintain a healthy lifestyle, or simply become more mindful of what you eat, this app is your trusted companion on your journey to better health.

Your heart powers every moment of your life. Heart Health Monitor & Tracker puts advanced heart monitoring, heart rate tracking, and pulse analysis right in your pocket—giving you the tools to take control of your cardiovascular health with ease and precision.

Key Features:
* Real-Time Heart Rate Monitoring Track your heart rate easily using your phone or connected devices with accurate, real-time readings.
* Daily Heart Health Reports Get clear, visual summaries of your heart activity, trends, and overall cardiovascular performance.
* Arrhythmia & Irregular Rhythm Alerts Receive notifications when the app detects signs of irregular heartbeats like AFib or skipped beats.
* Personalized Health Insights Understand your patterns and receive tailored advice based on your unique heart data and trends.
* Apple Health Integration Sync seamlessly with Apple Health and other compatible platforms for a complete health profile.

Why Choose Heart Health Monitor & Tracker? Designed for ease of use and backed by accurate data, this app is ideal for anyone looking to track heart performance, detect potential issues early, and live a heart-healthy life.

Download Heart Health Monitor & Tracker today and take the first step toward better heart health.


Disclaimer:
* Heart Health Monitor & Tracker is not a medical device and should not be used to diagnose heart conditions.
* Heart Health Monitor & Tracker is not intended for use in medical emergencies. Please consult your primary care physician if you require medical assistance.
* Heart Health Monitor & Tracker is NOT INTENDED FOR MEDICAL USE and is designed for fitness and general wellness purposes only.
* Heart Health Monitor & Tracker provides general health information and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
* The app may cause your phone’s LED flash to become very hot during use. Please use with caution.
